nodes.text: This marketplace was a location in Cuipernam, the capital city of Ansion. In 22 BBY, Jedi Master Luminara Unduli, Jedi Knight Obi-Wan Kenobi, and their Padawans Barriss Offee and Anakin Skywalker explored this marketplace during the Mission to Ansion. While in the marketplace, Offee was lured into a shop and drugged by Kyakhta and Bulgan, two clanless Ansionian males on the order of Soergg the Hutt, who wished to prevent the Jedi from completing their mission, which was to ensure Ansion did not secede from the Galactic Republic.
